{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"subtitle","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)subtitle"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"copy"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This string is displayed in the callout for the associated annotation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/subtitle":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle","title":"subtitle","abstract":[{"text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"}}}